{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231611, "create_time": 1655557143, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "以前有幸在盐湖城听过管风琴，也在亚洲姓氏谱牒中心遇到几位很好的华人学者。宗教的确有让人平和且向上的力量，那里信教的人都很优秀。我也曾参与过几次团契和弥撒，但都是以旁观者的身份，基督的种子无法在我心中生根发芽。", "timestamp": 1655557143}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231615, "create_time": 1655557202, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: alice现在美国留学吗？", "timestamp": 1655557202}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231618, "create_time": 1655557264, "is_blocked": true, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "", "timestamp": 1655557264}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231619, "create_time": 1655557280, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 6年前的事儿了，早就回来了", "timestamp": 1655557280}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231632, "create_time": 1655557475, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 你是以前有个洞的dz？识别出来了", "timestamp": 1655557475}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231634, "create_time": 1655557506, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 看宗教的发展和分布还蛮有意思的，我在芝加哥接触了很多华人基督团体，感觉很多大爷大妈还在用因果报应的思路理解爱人。所以，他们给我的感觉是：主让我来爱你，但我本人不爱你。而且华人基督徒，包括台湾基督徒，都很热衷于发展新教徒。韩国和美国基督徒就没这种倾向，也可能是我接触的不多吧……", "timestamp": 1655557506}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231637, "create_time": 1655557557, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 不懂，最近刚开始用上这个，只回帖，还没发过洞", "timestamp": 1655557557}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231647, "create_time": 1655557657, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 新教就是这样的吧…我在人大的高中同学也是新教徒，有次想跟他们牧师来清华传教。想要向我借学生卡，我怕惹事就拒绝了", "timestamp": 1655557657}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231660, "create_time": 1655557708, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 有个人说自己本科毕业去美国留学，现在又来清华读博，怀疑是你hhh", "timestamp": 1655557708}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 231703, "create_time": 1655558007, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 哈哈类似经历的人很多的~火锅和饺子多好吃啊", "timestamp": 1655558007}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 232062, "create_time": 1655561212, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 你说的那个dz是Bob哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1655561212}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 232063, "create_time": 1655561221, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Carol: 诶，看来是Carol了", "timestamp": 1655561221}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 232071, "create_time": 1655561340, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Carol: 我身边认识蛮多在国外读本硕，然后在清华读博的~\n回到dz的话题，我不信教，但是确实蛮喜欢基督教的氛围的~\n\n圣诞节是我最喜欢的节日，然后之前有参加过唱诗班，很喜欢唱宗教歌曲（确实很好听）\n但不妨碍我是一个坚定地无产主义者哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1655561340}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 232206, "create_time": 1655562940, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 我和基督教的接触也是从音乐开始的，以前在合唱团排练了很多作品，hallelujah，kyrie和ave maria之类的，那段排练的回忆很美好~说起来，我脱离教会团契活动是因为一个台湾大叔不厌其烦的联系我入教，后来我说我信仰马列主义和毛泽东思想……之后教会再没人联系我了哈哈", "timestamp": 1655562940}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 232218, "create_time": 1655563185, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 我也被新教徒传教xs \n那也许你可以了解一下天主教，没有人会劝你入教\n新教那种团契内部的氛围还是亲密的，不过只要你不再参加了，就不会再有人联系你了，好像之前的交情都不存在哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1655563185}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 232221, "create_time": 1655563228, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 我是真的不喜欢这种不厌其烦的宣传", "timestamp": 1655563228}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 232244, "create_time": 1655563666, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 嗯以前去过天津西开天主教堂，那边的神父都挺和善的，的确感觉很好。", "timestamp": 1655563666}], "create_time": 1655556453, "cw": "宗教相关", "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1655563666, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 17, "pid": 67960, "poll": null, "reply": 17, "text": "百无聊赖开始翻相册，回忆起了很多几乎淡忘掉的事情。\n记得疫情前的圣诞节，我去了西直门天主堂望弥撒。出身于天主教家庭，不过因为一些原因（也许有人会猜到吧）并不信仰宗教了，那次单纯陪舅舅去的。尽管如此，不知道为啥总是能从弥撒中获得心灵的安宁，可能是宗教给人的心理暗示吧。\n本科期间也没去过几次，只记得西直门的一位神父弹奏的管风琴很好听，还有个曾经在美国和伊拉克当记者的大叔的故事很精彩。\n后来再也没有去过西直门天主堂了，明明是两三年前的事情，却恍如隔世。\n\n\n![](https://gateway.pinata.cloud/ipfs/bafybeifulsiwhw3zkhyg55ftzarptipwkxzh5w534s6bsr7koohh7todym?filename=mmexport1655554440906.jpg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://thuhollow.github.io/ipfs.html#bafybeifulsiwhw3zkhyg55ftzarptipwkxzh5w534s6bsr7koohh7todym)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1655556453}}